#   R960 round-number commit landmark), Ixion (R956 171st),
#   KernelScript (R952 170th — round-number 170th-language
#   milestone), Prog8 (R948 169th), Objeck (R944 168th), Feral
#   (R940 167th — R940 round-number commit landmark), Biscuit/
#   BL (R936 166th), Rux (R932 165th), Jule (R928 164th),
#   Nevalang (R924 163rd), Corvid (R920 162nd — round-number
#   R920 commit landmark), Soppo (R916 161st), Cyrus (R912
#   160th — round-number language milestone), Lumina (R908
#   159th), Penne (R904 158th), EndBASIC (R900 157th — R900
#   TRIPLE-9 commit landmark), goboscript (R896 156th), Alan
#   (R892 155th), Mech (R888 154th — triple-8 landmark),
#   Lisette (R884 153rd), Bril (R880 152nd), Vyxal (R876
#   151st), EYG (R872 150th — round-number language
